articles.author: April Rubin
articles.title: White House: Report Abrego Garcia will be deported again "fake news" - Axios
articles.description: A spokesperson said he will "face the full force of the American justice system."
articles.content:
The latest: White House spokesperson Abigail Jackson, responding to an AP report on what prosecutors said about deporting Abrego Garcia again, posted on X: "This is fake news."
